    "name": "SakhaPR Prescreen Question Sets",
    "source": "List pertanyaan prescreen interview awal (UOB KPR)",
    "compiled_on": "2026-06-20",
    "language": "id-ID",
    "usage": "After intent is READY_TO_APPLY, pick the set by product (decision_routing), run questions one at a time, store answers in memory, then produce file a (.txt). Honour 'conditional': skip a question if its dependency is not met. 'flag_hint' lets the assistant raise an early signal (e.g. risk) for the sales side; it is NOT a credit decision.",
    "disclaimer": "Interview awal ini hanya untuk triase awal, bukan keputusan kredit. Keputusan akhir mengikuti analisa kredit dan Perjanjian Kredit."
